waitingThreadJobsDesc - The number of messages currently being processed by waiting pooly processor threads.
waitingThreadsDesc - The number of threads currently processing messages that had to wait for a resource.

panels.content:
# Distributed System Messaging [DistributionStats](http://gemfire.docs.pivotal.io/geode/reference/statistics/statistics_list.html#section_ACB4161F10D64BC0B15871D003FF6FDF)
Statistics on the Geode distribution layer. These statistics can be used to tell how much message traffic exists between this member and other distributed system members.
panels.title: DistributionStat

panels.description:
ucastReads - Total number of unicast datagrams received.
ucastWrites - Total number of unicast datagram socket write calls.
panels.title: UCAST Read/Write

panels.description:
ucastReadBytes - Total number of bytes received in unicast datagrams.
ucastWriteBytes - Total number of bytes sent out on unicast datagram sockets.
panels.title: UCAST Read/Write Bytes

panels.description: ucastWriteTime - Total amount of time, in nanoseconds, spent in unicast datagram socket write calls.
panels.title: UCAST Write Time

panels.description:
syncSocketWrites - Total number of completed synchronous/blocking socket write calls.

syncSocketWritesInProgress - Current number of synchronous/blocking socket write calls in progress.
panels.title: Sync Socket Writes

panels.description: syncSocketWriteBytes  - Total number of bytes sent out in synchronous/blocking mode on sockets.
panels.title: Sync Socket Write Bytes

panels.description: syncSocketWriteTime - Total amount of time, in nanoseconds, spent in synchronous/blocking socket write calls.
panels.title: Sync Socket Write Time

panels.description: socketLocks	Total number of times a socket has been locked
panels.title: Socket Locks

panels.description: socketLockTime	Total amount of time, in nanoseconds, spent locking a socket.
panels.title: Socket Locks Time

panels.description: serialThreads - The number of threads currently processing serial/ordered messages.
panels.title: Serial Threads

panels.description:
serializations	Total number of object serialization calls. 

deserializations	Total number of object deserialization calls.
panels.title: Serialization/Deserialization

panels.description:
serializationTime	Total amount of time, in nanoseconds, spent serializing objects.
deserializationTime	Total amount of time, in nanoseconds, spent deserializing objects.
panels.title: Serialization/Deserialization Times

panels.description:
deserializedBytes	Total number of bytes consumed by object deserialization.
serializedBytes	Total number of bytes produced by object serialization.
panels.title: Serialized/Deserialized Bytes

panels.description:
pdxSerializations	Total number of PDX serializations.

pdxDeserializations	Total number of PDX deserializations.
panels.title: PDX Serializations/Deserializations

panels.description:
pdxInstanceCreations	Total number of times a PdxInstance has been created by deserialization.

pdxInstanceDeserializations	Total number of times getObject has been called on a PdxInstance.
panels.title: PDX Instance Creation/Deserializations

panels.description:
pdxSerializedBytes	Total number of bytes produced by PDX serialization.

pdxDeserializedBytes	Total number of bytes read by PDX deserialization.
panels.title: PDX Serialization/Deserializations Bytes

panels.description: pdxInstanceDeserializationTime Total amount of time, in nanoseconds, spent deserializing PdxInstances by calling getObject
panels.title: PDX Index Deserializations Time

panels.description:
sentMessages	The number of distribution messages that the Geode system has sent, which includes broadcastMessages.

receivedMessages	The number of distribution messages that the Geode system has received.
panels.title: Sent/Received Messages

panels.description:
sentMessagesTimeDesc	The total amount of time this distribution manager has spent sending messages, which includes broadcastMessagesTime.

sentMessagesMaxTimeDesc	The highest amount of time this distribution manager has spent distributing a single message to the network.

receivedMessages	The number of distribution messages that the Geode system has received.

seriesOverrides.alias: max sent message time for single message

targets.alias: max sent message time for single message

panels.title: Sent Messages Time

panels.description:
replyMessageTime The amount of time spent processing reply messages;

replyWaitMaxTime	Maximum time spent transmitting and then waiting for a reply to a message. See sentMessagesMaxTime for related information.
panels.title: Reply Message Time

panels.description:
sentBytes The number of distribution message bytes that the Geode system has sent.

receivedBytes The number of distribution message bytes that the Geode system has received.
panels.title: Sent / Received Bytes

panels.description:
senderDirectBufferSize	Current number of bytes allocated from direct memory as buffers for outgoing messages.

receiverDirectBufferSizeDesc	Current number of bytes allocated from direct memory as buffers for incoming messages
panels.title: Sender/Receiver Direct BufferSize

panels.description:
senderTimeouts	Total number of message sent that have timed out.

replyTimeouts	Total number of message replies that have timed out.
panels.title: Sender/Reply Message Timeouts

panels.description:
replyWaitsCompleted	Total number of times waits for a reply have completed.

replyWaitsInProgress	Current number of threads waiting for a reply.
panels.title: Reply Waits Completed/In-Progress

panels.description:
processedMessages	The number of distribution messages that the Geode system has processed.
processedMessagesTime	The amount of time this distribution manager has spent in message.process().
panels.title: Processed Messages Count / Time

panels.description:
processingThreadJobs - The number of messages currently being processed by pooled message processor threads.

processingThreads - The number of threads currently processing normal messages.

processingThreadStarts - Total number of times a thread has been created for the pool processing normal messages.
panels.title: Processing Threads

panels.description:
partitionedRegionThreadJobsDesc	The number of messages currently being processed by partitioned region threads.

partitionedRegionThreadsDesc	The number of threads currently processing partitioned region messages.
panels.title: Partitioned Region Threads

panels.description: nodes	The current number of members in this distributed system.
panels.title: Nodes

panels.description:
msgDeserialization Total amount of time, in nanoseconds, spent deserializing messages.

msgSerializationTime	Total amount of time, in nanoseconds, spent serializing messages.
panels.title: Msg Serialization/Deserialization Time

panels.description: messagesBeingReceived	Current number of messages being received off the network or being processed after reception.
panels.title: Messages Being Received

panels.description: messageBytesBeingReceived	Current number of bytes consumed by messages being received or processed.
panels.title: Message Bytes Being Received

panels.description:
messageChannelTime The total amount of time received messages spent in the distribution channel.

messageProcessingScheduleTime	The amount of time this distribution manager has spent dispatching a message to processor threads.
panels.title: Message Channel / Schedule Times

panels.description:
mcastRetransmitRequests	Total number of multicast datagram socket retransmission requests sent to other processes.

mcastRetransmits	Total number of multicast datagram socket retransmissions.
panels.title: MCAST Retransmits

panels.description:
broadcastMessages - The number of distribution messages that the Geode system has broadcast. A broadcast message is one sent to every other manager in the group.

broadcastMessagesTime - The total amount of time this distribution manager has spent broadcasting messages. A broadcast message is one sent to every other manager in the group.
panels.title: Broadcast Messages

panels.description: commitWaits	The number of transaction commits that had to wait for a response before they could complete.
panels.title: Commit Waits

panels.description:
highPriorityThreadJobs	The number of messages currently being processed by high priority processor threads.

highPriorityThreads	The number of threads currently processing high priority messages.

highPriorityThreadStarts	Total number of times a thread has been created for the pool handling high priority messages.
panels.title: High Priority Thread

panels.description:
mcastRetransmitRequests	Total number of multicast datagram socket retransmission requests sent to other processes.

mcastRetransmits	Total number of multicast datagram socket retransmissions.
panels.title: MCAST Retransmits
